item.dc:creator: @yppman yppman
item.description:
@yppman wrote:

You need to code it so that the button performs what the command would. Search for:case 161:in your client.java file. That and the next 20 or so cases below it are each activated when you click a certain one of the emote buttons. Youâ€™ll have to find which one is the one you need yourself and inbetween its : and break; add whatever is in your shop command.
